data.description: Get ready holidays are here. Jingle your way home to this 3/2.5 offering large master suite w/master bath updated w/granite counter tops & jacuzzi tub. Flooring updated in foyer, kitchen, family & formal dining! Upstairs are 2 bedrooms/bath. Enjoy your favorite drink on your back patio! Home has been re-piped, Ac/Furnace replaced Approx.. 3 yrs, new skylights. Walking distance to The Big A boat launch. This home has never Flooded!! Call your agents!
